{"tid":777752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「幫幫手」想追隔離班女仔...","createTime":"2018-08-13T06:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T09:52:56.000Z","uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6329c09ee89b3b5edf282c8bdf9f3b883f2aaa47","tid":777752,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"我今年讀緊中三，下年升中四，從未試過拍拖,一直都係同班兄弟一齊玩吓,食吓飯, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出下街睇下戲咁,冇乜特別... <br />\n其實我已經喑戀咗佢差唔多都有2年,係一見中情果款鐘意... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我地真係冇乜緣份,我地屬於唔同小學入黎呢間中學讀, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就係面試成功入黎讀,而我就係由小學直升上黎讀! <br />\n升中一暑假果年考完個分班試之後,分為ABCD四班... <br />\n有一次上堂果陣,我太過貪玩唔小心太大力扯爛咗佢個草泥馬公仔條繩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時我心諗:今次大獲啦!我唔知點算好,於是就求其張佢個公仔dum落個書包就放學走人就算... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩佢果款公仔唔難買到...我第2日即刻走過去同佢道歉講對唔住同埋送返兩隻草泥馬公仔俾佢, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢起初都幾嬲,但後來佢可能覺得果2隻草泥馬公仔好得意,之後就同我微笑同埋講咗句多謝就走咗... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔計果次意外...基本上我同佢一句野都冇講過,我想認識佢,但唔知用咩方法好... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年識多咗好多唔同ge新朋友,但就係識唔到佢lor... <br />\n點先可以改變自己,吸引她注意!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係未試過同女仔熟,唔知佢點睇我呢,我應該點樣踏出第一步??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人資料如下:.... <br />\nInformation(我): <br />\n性格:為人比較cooL,靜,樂觀開朗,唔怕悶,守時,少量幽默感,少少爛口... 幾型下，有米八而且住私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n興趣:玩手機遊戲,打籃波，打保齡,飛鏢,計數,彈琴,聽歌(k-pop,中,英文歌),鐘意上網睇片等等... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係文靜,斯斯文文,温桑細心體貼果類型女仔! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢唔鐘意人有目的地接近佢扮熟想溝佢... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地大家都係各自各有班Friend一齊玩,所以約佢出街比較困難... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為下年就升中四了，想把握機會，唔該哂Thankyou!!!"},{"pid":"4e14628e642b00d04194c74d46ae57629e9e6c28","tid":777752,"uid":199871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"BECOME ANOTHER PERSON FIRST"},{"pid":"3600f21702b608f143a44c9f1f5233cce36a95c6","tid":777752,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e14628e642b00d04194c74d46ae57629e9e6c28","tid":777752,"uid":199871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"BECOME ANOTHER PERSON FIRST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"下年升中四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有排先可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78aa23ab83718f22989a8ef49f84838e69edd199","tid":777752,"uid":60552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146a291ff04d737b264bfdb155643aff0d10a2eb","tid":777752,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78aa23ab83718f22989a8ef49f84838e69edd199","tid":777752,"uid":60552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"做乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171773e253ef7116100f59cb2d30335eae7cc84b","tid":777752,"uid":136038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"考完古未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4894713&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4894713%26page%3D1&d=%2FjI2VTkhbvnYLJGZcMNtSzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5e978da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4894713&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"70ac32c45256a08ca76d168873307d8d84327d6d","tid":777752,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"171773e253ef7116100f59cb2d30335eae7cc84b","tid":777752,"uid":136038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"考完古未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4894713&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4894713%26page%3D1&d=%2FjI2VTkhbvnYLJGZcMNtSzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&